{
  "stem": "747.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my son said, call up the Italian consulate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She lives in Genoa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the back of the book is the information with a picture.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And within a half an hour, they called me back with her number.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote to her a letter and you [? saw ?] the beautiful letter she wrote to me, thanking me to come back to her life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure, sure, we were together and she remembers this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, she remembers this incidents, what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While she was-- I was lucky I was liberated by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was stopped on the other side of Schwerin, and was ended up by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's another story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And little by little, got back to Italy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She didn't find anyone and nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she started right away to-- she was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's a newspaper woman, and well-known.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a friend of--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liana Millu, M-I-L-L-U.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started to correspond with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got a very warm response.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I invited her to come and visit us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she wrote that she's too old to travel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe one day we will meet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my son, who was longing to go back to Italy to see the birthplace where he was born, decided that we will go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Renee, my daughter-in-law came along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the three of us did a trip last May.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was an experience that I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We find the room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the garden I showed here--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grugliasco.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then a stranger took us into Torino.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They find a hospital where he was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we met Liana in Genoa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful reunion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we are in touch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're corresponding.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
